               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the archangels Gäbrǝʾel and Mikaʾel (fols. 24ra, 25ra); elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Texts I-1, I-4 (alternating with black lines); two initial lines in the incipit of Text I-5; two initial lines in the incipit of the subsections (miracles); first word of Text I-3.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-3 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Maryam [wäladitä ʾamlak] ... "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, [Godbearing] ..." (fols. 10va l.23-11ra l.9)</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Maryam ʾǝmmu lä-ʾǝgziʾǝnä ʾIyäsus Krǝstos kähali ... "O my Lady Mary, Mother of our Lord Jesus Christ the Almighty ..." (fol. 11ra l.9-11rb l.2) (cp. ChRep no. 373)</note>
                     <note>- Sälam läki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Maryam ʾǝmmä bǝrhan ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady Mary, Mother of the Light ..." (fols. 11rb l.2-vb).</note>
                  </msItem>
